#

Chicken Tortilla Soup

45 min
$12
320 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupEasyComfort Food

Description

A comforting and flavorful soup packed with chicken, beans, and topped with crispy tortilla strips.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 2 cups, shredded
  • canned diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • black beans: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • chicken broth: 4 cups
  • corn kernels: 1 cup, frozen or fresh
  • tortilla chips: 1 cup
  • avocado: 1, diced
  • cheddar cheese: 1 cup, shredded
  • lime: 1, juiced
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
